    feat2812:
        "Assassin's Challenge Heroic Tier Prerequisite : Assassin, paladin, assassin's shroud power Benefit : You can use a holy symbol as an implement. In addition, whenever a creature takes damage from your divine challenge power, that creature takes 1 extra damage for each of your assassin's shrouds on it. Dragon Magazine 385, page(s) 34.",
    feat1785:
        "Assassin's Cloak Heroic Tier Prerequisite : Assassin Benefit : Whenever you become invisible, you can make a Stealth check to hide as a free action. Dragon Magazine 379, page(s) 26.",
