        "Enshrouding Touch Heroic Tier Prerequisite : Gnome, paladin, lay on hands or virtue's touch power Benefit : Each ally targeted by your lay on hands or virtue's touch power gains concealment until the end of his or her next turn. Dragon Magazine 384, page(s) 60.",
