        "Envoy to the Fey Heroic Tier Prerequisite : Bard Benefit : You can speak, read, and write Elven. When you make a Bluff, Diplomacy, Intimidate, or Streetwise check against a fey creature, you can roll twice and use the higher result. Dragon Magazine 387, page(s) 25.",
