        "Retributive Shield Heroic Tier Prerequisite : Swordmage with aegis of shielding Benefit : When you use your aegis of shielding power, you gain a +2 bonus to the next attack roll made before the end of your next turn against the foe that triggered the aegis of shielding immediate interrupt. Forgotten Realms Player's Guide, page(s) 136.",
