    feat1158:
        "Rune-Scribed Soul Heroic Tier Prerequisite : Dwarf, any arcane class Benefit : When you use your second wind, you gain a +1 bonus to attack rolls and a bonus to damage equal to your Constitution modifier with arcane powers you use before the end of your turn. Arcane Power, page(s) 129.",
