        "Sambrese Rake Heroic Tier Prerequisite : Windrise Ports regional background Benefit : You gain a +3 bonus to Bluff checks made to gain combat advantage and can reroll each such check once. You must use the second result. Also, when you succeed on such a check, you can shift 1 square as part of the action. Dragon Magazine 376, page(s) 50.",
